# CSPR-Depth

This repository contains the official implementation of:

**CSPR-Depth: Context-Preserved Structural Reasoning for Sharp Monocular Depth Estimation in Low-Texture Scenes**

## News

The source code is currently being cleaned, organized, and documented.  
We will release the complete codebase, pretrained models, and evaluation scripts to facilitate reproducibility.

## Release Plan

- Training and inference code
- Pretrained model weights
- Evaluation scripts
- Dataset preparation instructions
- Visualization examples

## Citation

If you find this work useful, please consider citing our paper.  
The BibTeX entry will be updated after publication.
